{
  "title": "Intriguing Yeasty Indian Lentils Dal Tadka",
  "description": "A yeasty and silky Indian lentil dish featuring dark soy sauce, toast, and a blend of spices, perfect for adventurous eaters. This nut-free-friendly dal tadka is a unique twist on traditional Tamil cuisine.",
